        <h1>Text Instructions</h1>
        <h3>Getting started</h3>
        <p>1. Head over to the <a href="https://github.com/dradis/dradis-ce">Dradis Framework repo</a> on GitHub.</p>
        <p>2. On your local system, run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ git clone https://github.com/dradis/dradis-ce.git</code><br/><code>$ cd dradis-ce/</code></p>
        <p>3. Run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ bundle install</code></p>
        <p>4. Run the following in your command line:<br/><code>$ ./bin/setup</code></p>
      </div>
